OL,3,COlivia Dean triumphs with triple win
OL,4,Cat Mobo Awards
OL,6,FSinger Olivia Dean took home three
OL,7,Fmajor awards at the 30th anniversary
OL,8,Fof the MOBOs.
OL,10,FThe landmark ceremony, which
OL,11,Fcelebrates the very best in Black
OL,12,Fmusic and culture, was held at
OL,13,FManchester's Co-op Live arena for the
OL,14,Ffirst time on Thursday, 26 March.
OL,16,FIt marked three decades since the MOBO
OL,17,F(Music of Black Origin) organisation
OL,18,Fwas first established.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
