OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774714286
OL,3,COlivia Dean triumphs with triple win
OL,4,Cat Mobo Awards
OL,6,FDean emerged as the most decorated
OL,7,Fartist of the evening, securing wins
OL,8,Fin three prestigious categories: Song
OL,9,Fof the Year for her hit single 'Man I
OL,10,FNeed', Album of the Year for her debut
OL,11,F'The Art of Loving' and Best Female
OL,12,FAct.
OL,14,FThis latest haul continues a
OL,15,Fremarkable winning streak for the
OL,16,FLondon-born singer after she took home
OL,17,Ffour trophies at the Brit Awards, held
OL,18,Fat the same Manchester venue at the
OL,19,Fend of February.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
