PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774714286
OL,3,COlivia Dean triumphs with triple win
OL,4,Cat Mobo Awards
OL,6,FThe MOBO lifetime achievement award
OL,7,Fwas given to British-American rapper
OL,8,Fand record producer Slick Rick.
OL,10,FHe said: "It's a great honour.
OL,11,FAppreciated me from where I come from,
OL,12,Fso thank you very much, Manchester. I
OL,13,Fappreciate the love."
OL,15,FHe took to the stage with singer
OL,16,FEstelle for a collaborative
OL,17,Fperformance to showcase his hip hop
OL,18,Fjourney.
OL,26,@rD@JOUuD@UO]
