PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774714286
OL,3,COlivia Dean triumphs with triple win
OL,4,Cat Mobo Awards
OL,6,FSpeaking ahead of the show, Estelle
OL,7,Fsaid it was "amazing" to be in
OL,8,FManchester for the first time in the
OL,9,Fceremony's history.
OL,11,FShe said: "I'm like, what took it so
OL,12,Flong to get to Manchester? But
OL,13,Feverything at the right time..."
OL,15,FShe added: "We're here, we're
OL,16,Fcelebrating us and that's beautiful."
OL,18,FThe global songwriter award was given
OL,19,Fto American musician Pharrell Williams.
OL,26,@oD@MOUoD@UO]sD@KOUuD@`O]wD@LOUxD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
