OL,3,COlivia Dean triumphs with triple win
OL,4,Cat Mobo Awards
OL,6,FManchester-based singer-songwriter
OL,7,FDaley, who collaborated with Williams
OL,8,Fon the 2014 song 'Look Up', said he
OL,9,Fwas thoroughly deserving of the award.
OL,11,FHe said: "It was very clear to me why
OL,12,Fhe's such a successful and such a good
OL,13,Fsongwriter because he really taps into
OL,14,Fwhat the feeling of the song is, so
OL,15,Fhe's very deserving."
OL,17,FDC3 claimed two awards ` for best
OL,18,Fnewcomer and best gospel ` and was
OL,19,Fthere to celebrate with his family. He
OL,20,Fsaid the "meaningful" awards came as a
OL,21,Fshock to him.
OL,26,@sD@JOUwD@UO]|D@JOU|D@UO]
