PN,39907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774714286
OL,3,COlivia Dean triumphs with triple win
OL,4,Cat Mobo Awards
OL,6,F"Beyond the trophy itself, it's a very
OL,7,Fspecial thing that a name like Ezra
OL,8,FCollective can get mentioned and lots
OL,9,Fof people recognise it and that's
OL,10,Ftestament to so many people supporting
OL,11,Fus, from grassroots and championing
OL,12,Fus."
OL,14,FKirkby-born actor Stephen Graham won
OL,15,Fbest performance in a TV show or film
OL,16,Ffor Adolescence.
OL,18,FOn the red carpet, stars said the
OL,19,Fawards continued to be important 30
OL,20,Fyears after it was founded.
OL,26,@tD@DO]
